data.description: Great work from home set up! Home is fully wired w/ ethernet throughout the home and garage. Exterior cameras and server rack in garage are included. Granite kitchen w/ stainless steel appliance package and soft close cabinetry. All kitchen appliances and washer/dryer are included. Utility room is conveniently upstairs! This home has nice laminate wood and carpet flooring, eating bar, dining, and a cozy gas fireplace in living room. Outdoor privacy fence and underground irrigation on this large corner lot.
